ckchain and crypto. For <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">now<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> the <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Binance<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> CEO expects Musk <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">has<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> other concerns. <\/span><\/span><span class=\"LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><br class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\n<\/span><span class=\"LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><br class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\n<\/span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\u201CMusk has a lot of people to fire, lots of things to change,\u201D he said.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><br class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\n<\/span><span class=\"LineBreakBlob BlobObject DragDrop SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><br class=\"SCXW31950071 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\n<\/span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW31950071 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndG